Beautiful home in the Bonnell West Subdivision. The quality and attention to detail abound in this home featuring 4 Bedrooms, 3 Baths, Office + Bonus Room. Beautiful cherry cabinetry in the gourmet kitchen and living room. The kitchen opens up to a nicely landscaped back yard and large deck. The whole house attic fan is fantastic! All the bedrooms have lots of light and the Master Bedroom has vaulted ceilings with a spacious 5 piece luxury bath. The basement is garden level with lots of light.





