Back on market, Walk into this beautiful single family home, through the foyer into a spacious opening, living room, gorgeous new ceramic tiled flooring, new island, new counter tops, new back splash, large cabinets and freshly painted kitchen with other amenities. Seller to include new sewer lateral in purchase of property. Property located walking distance, 1/4 to 1/2 mile from park, restaurants, short driving distance to Forest Park, Central West End, Botanical Garden, Down Town area and many other sights. Property to be sold in AS-IS condition, seller may.... consider paying some closing cost. Agents, seller is motivated to sell property, please bring all reasonable offers!





