Real Estate Market Trends in Loveland, CO

    The median price home price in Loveland is $425,000. Right now, there are 655 homes listed for sale in Loveland, including 57 condos and 1 foreclosures. You can research home values, browse Loveland's hottest homes, and see what Coldwell Banker's agents have to say about the local area. Check out our page on Loveland market trends  to start exploring!
  











