Product Description

A comfortable T-shirt that features a stylish, deeper plunged neck than the traditional V-neck.

100% Sheer Jersey construction (Heather Grey contains 10% Polyester)
Durable rib deep V-neckband
Unisex size – women may prefer to order one size smaller
Fabric weight 3.8 oz/yd² (129 g/m²)
Good screen printing results




